    public class KeyValueTable
extends AbstractDataset
implements BatchReadable<byte[],byte[]>, BatchWritable<byte[],byte[]>, RecordScannable<KeyValue<byte[],byte[]>>, RecordWritable<KeyValue<byte[],byte[]>>
    A key/value map implementation on top of Table supporting read, write and delete operations.

        Returns splits for a range of keys in the table.
        Parameters:
        numSplits - Desired number of splits. If greater than zero, at most this many splits will be returned. If less than or equal to zero, any number of splits can be returned.
